text: No issue with service or wait time. There are only 2 people working and grilling food takes time. Taste wise ok but not exceptional. Packaging wise, not sure why they choose to use small packaging which forces them to break the fish up for takeaway orders. Not a deal breaker though.

Now, we know why waiting time is so long even though there's only 1 Food Order.

Cos that slim lady with glasses was sitting behind the counter having her meal. And when being asked, she said 2 minutes with that unhappy expression.

Sohai~

ordered fish and chips and the fish was smelly and not fresh at all. it was mostly just the batter too. and the potato salad was terrible too. as someone who doesnt like wasting food i just couldnt bring myself to finish this. WORST WESTERN FOOD EVER!!

author_name: Patriarchy of the western cat realm
text: Im all for supporting local and all. Life is tough but so are others. To give such thinly sliced chicken and charging $8.90 for it. You are passing on the toughness to the next person. :(( i wish to support and come back again, but i need to fill my stomach and have energy to go to work.
Good western food, taste was great. But at prices higher than Tenderbest. Will go again since there was a discount offer.
